{
  "stem": "1917.5",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 391.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But if I'm the president of some kind of an organization, that's a good way to do it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So I did that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I put together-- and I wrote my sister that I'm going to make her vice president for the Israeli survivors.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And she said, don't put me in any kind of lectures.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I don't speak.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I don't want to lecture anywhere.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I said, no, you just have to kind of help me find the twins in Israel.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And what happened was that I happened to be working for the first time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had a lot of trouble getting a job as a realtor, because I quit drafting, and I got my license as a realtor, and I started going to college to get my college degree.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in Terre Haute, Indiana, it's a very provincial in many ways.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they said, with an accent like you cannot sell real estate.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I worked for a very small company, then I would earn like $2,000 a year.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And at the time, the kids were in junior high and high school.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they needed clothes and everything else.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were trying to save some money for college.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I had to work two other jobs to make the same money that I made as a draftsperson before that.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I wanted to stay with it and I was not going to quit.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, I am not going to ever quit real estate unless I am a success, because I don't ever want to look back at something that I did and look at it as a failure.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And for six years, I was a complete failure.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then I kept knocking on the same doors.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And finally, somebody said yes, big company-- the largest company in town.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
